text: Nvidia Corporation’s stock (NVDA) rose in the intraday levels, amid the dominance of the main upward trend in the medium term, while trading alongside the secondary short-term trend line, with positive pressure from the 50-day SMA, coupled with positive signals from the RSI after reaching oversold levels.  Therefore we expect more gains for the stock, targeting the resistance of 880.50, provided the support of 744.00 holds on.  Expected trend for today: Bullish
